snippet.title: Sky Fleet - Official Trailer | PAX Online 2021
snippet.description:
Take a look at Sky Fleet, a co-op shooter, tower defense, and base building game about defending your floating islands from invaders. Build a city and gather resources so that you can fight the invaders back.
